类 ImageService

java.lang.Object
model.ImageService
public class ImageService extends Object
Service class for handling image-related operations in the recipe management system. This class provides functionality for image file manipulation, validation, and storage.
从以下版本开始:
1.0

  • 方法详细资料

    • duplicateImage

      public Path duplicateImage(String imageUrl)
      Duplicates an image file to the project's image directory with a unique timestamp-based name. This method copies the source image to the dishes directory and renames it to avoid conflicts.
      参数:
      imageUrl - the path or URL of the source image file
      返回:
      the Path object pointing to the duplicated image file, or null if operation failed

    • isValidURL

      public boolean isValidURL(String url)
      Validates whether a given string is a valid URL format. Supports HTTP, HTTPS, FTP, and file protocols.
      参数:
      url - the URL string to validate
      返回:
      true if the URL format is valid, false otherwise
